title: Project Lucky: Samsung Galaxy S7 details start to leak
text: Timing is everything. Apple unveiled the the iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus yesterday. Today, the first details of the Samsung Galaxy S7 have leaked. The early leak comes courtesy of SamMobile, which refers to a Samsung smartphone called “Lucky-LTE” that recently appeared on the Geekbench benchmark database.
